fields.description:
*Environment:*
Public version 1.1.16.3
Lenovo Tablet P11 Plus
Android version - 12

Steps to reproduce:
1. Perform Total analysis
2. After analysis go to Settings screen.
3. Select Data Synchronization menu
4. Count of images to be uploaded should be displayed
5. Click the “Send” button
6. Click again the “Send” button
7. Click again the “Send” button

Expected result: That it will no longer upload after the count of images is reached.

Actual result: It will keep sending images until counts goes over the original image count.

*Attachment:*

!image-20221206-065211.png|width=1002,height=540!
fields.summary: Settings[Data Synchronization]: Image uploaded will double when clicking "Send" button multiple times
